{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/dawn-theme-clickable-banner-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1339,"date":"2022-01-13T10:36:10","date_gmt":"2022-01-13T10:36:10","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1339"},"modified":"2023-03-19T21:50:11","modified_gmt":"2023-03-19T21:50:11","slug":"dawn-theme-clickable-banner-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/dawn-theme-clickable-banner-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"How to make the image banner clickable [all free themes]"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Are you trying to make your Dawn theme&#8217;s banner section image clickable? Look no further! Although the Dawn&#8217;s banner section comes with buttons that you can add links to, there is no way to make the image itself clickable. Well, up until now! <br><br>With this guide I&#8217;ll teach you how you can make your banner clickable just by pasting some code into your theme. <br><br><a href=\"https://pandashopdeals.myshopify.com/pages/clickable-banner\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live preview of how the end result will look like.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"NoticeBox NoticeBox--info\"><p>This tutorial is compatible with all Shopify&#8217;s official free themes: <b>Dawn, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Origin, Publisher, Sense &amp; Craft.</b></p></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-current-theme\">Making a backup of your current theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-code-to-your-theme\">Adding the code to your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>From your Shopify Admin go to: <strong>online store &gt; themes &gt; actions &gt; edit code</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Find the file named exactly <strong>&#8220;image-banner.liquid&#8221;</strong><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"789\" height=\"498\" class=\"wp-image-1429\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/x11.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/x11.jpg 789w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/x11-768x485.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 789px) 100vw, 789px\" /></li>\n\n\n\n<li>In this file, press <strong>CTRL + F</strong> (or <strong>CMD + F</strong> on <strong>Mac</strong>) to open the search bar. <br><br>Search for exactly this (space included):<br><br><strong>label_1 |</strong><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>A piece of code will be highlighted around line 122. (Don&#8217;t worry if it&#8217;s not this exact number)<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1360\" height=\"836\" class=\"wp-image-2613\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_23.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_23.jpg 1360w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_23-850x523.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_23-1200x738.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_23-768x472.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Paste the following code right below the <strong>&lt;/a&gt;</strong>, which is below the line you found. Please check the images below for a clearer reference.<br><br>[gist]9d05cbe550b28576ea2652a00f5e6984[gist]<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1358\" height=\"851\" class=\"wp-image-2615\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_24.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_24.jpg 1358w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_24-850x533.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_24-1200x752.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_24-768x481.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1358px) 100vw, 1358px\" /><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1470\" height=\"878\" class=\"wp-image-2617\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_25.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_25.jpg 1470w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_25-850x508.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_25-1200x717.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_25-768x459.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1470px) 100vw, 1470px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Don&#8217;t forget to click on the &#8220;save&#8221; button on the top right.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-checking-if-it-s-working\">Checking if it&#8217;s working</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>From the &#8220;Customize&#8221; page, click on the &#8220;Image Banner&#8221; section and on &#8220;Buttons&#8221;.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1077\" height=\"612\" class=\"wp-image-2619\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/button1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/button1.jpg 1077w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/button1-850x483.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/button1-768x436.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1077px) 100vw, 1077px\" /><br></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Make sure that the &#8220;First button link&#8221; is populated. Click on the save button and it should be all good.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1265\" height=\"624\" class=\"wp-image-2621\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_26.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_26.jpg 1265w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_26-850x419.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_26-1200x592.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Screenshot_26-768x379.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1265px) 100vw, 1265px\" /></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other tutorials you may be interested in. They work with &#8220;Dawn&#8221; plus all Shopify&#8217;s free themes (Craft, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Origin, Publisher &amp; Sense):<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Arrows &amp; vertical thumbnails for Dawn&#8217;s product pages<span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/w4LaQF8cp1akInO4Cp/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-how-to-fix-zoom-images-size-mobile-desktop?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Dawn lightbox: responsive images, slider and arrows <span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media4.giphy.com/media/aBmvXTlfvHiPMXtx4a/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Improve your website&#8217;s safety: block right click, image copying and more</a></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to make the original Dawn theme&#8217;s banner clickable without heavy customizations.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1351,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[655,626,657,435,776,773,663,649,652,646,660],"acf":[],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/debut_slideshow-5-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/debut_slideshow-5-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/debut_slideshow-5-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Colorblock Theme","Craft Theme","Crave Theme","Dawn Theme","origin theme","publisher theme","Refresh theme","Ride theme","Sense Theme","Studio Theme","Taste theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/debut_slideshow-5.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1339"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1339"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1339/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2628,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1339/revisions/2628"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/1351"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1339"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=1339"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?